ation: Freeing slaves rewarded with protection from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhenever a Muslim man emancipates a Muslim man, he will be his freedom from Hellfire; he will be rewarded for every limb of his in equal measure. Whenever a Muslim man emancipates two Muslim women, they will be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25265,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/11\/care-for-orphans-free-slaves\/","url_meta":{"origin":25269,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Orphans: Care for the orphans, free the slaves","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Malik ibn Al-Harith reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever embraces an orphan of two Muslim parents by feeding him and giving him drink until he is independent of him, Paradise will certainly be necessary for him. Whoever emancipates a Muslim man, he will\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26265,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/04\/24\/umar-on-slaves-umm-walad-is-emancipated-when-her-master-dies\/","url_meta":{"origin":25269,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Slaves: Umm walad is emancipated when her master dies","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 24, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhen a servant woman gives birth from her master, then he may not sell her, or bestow her, or bequeath her. He may enjoy her and she becomes free when he dies.\u201d Source: al-Muwat\u0323t\u0323a\u2019 1509 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4343,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/06\/prophet-frees-marries-safiyyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25269,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: The Prophet frees Safiyyah, marries her","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 6, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, emancipated Safiyyah, married her, and regarded her freedom as her dowry. The Prophet held a banquet with sweet dishes. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 4798, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1365 Grade: Muttafaqun\u00a0Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3791,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/24\/muslim-who-fasts-distant-hellfire\/","url_meta":{"origin":25269,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: A Muslim who fasts will be distant from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said,\u00a0\"Whoever fasts a day in the way of Allah, Allah will move his face away from the Hellfire by a distance of seventy years.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2840, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1153 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8395,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/16\/prophet-frees-slaves-taif\/","url_meta":{"origin":25269,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Freedom: The Prophet frees the slaves of al-Ta&#8217;if","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: When the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, besieged the people of Al-Ta\u2019if, he freed their slaves who came out to him. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 3257 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u0627\u0635\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadi